{"tid":665396,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【暴動罪審訊】官引導陪審團判罪","createTime":"2018-05-15T02:05:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T02:09:03.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bf9e9bf66582a1e0a6503bce7fe1acee85334400","tid":665396,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T02:05:47.000Z","msg":"(法官) 彭寶琴解釋，根據《公安條例》第18（1）條，凡有3人或多於3人集結在一起，作出擾亂秩序的行為，或作出帶有威嚇性、侮辱性或挑撥性的行為，意圖導致或相當可能導致任何人合理地害怕如此集結的人會破壞社會安寧，或害怕他們會藉以上的行為激使其他人破壞社會安寧，他們即屬非法集結；而根據條例第18（2）條，集結的人如作出如上述般的行為，則即使其原來的集結是合法的，亦無關重要。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E7%BD%AA%E5%AF%A9%E8%A8%8A-%E5%AE%98%E5%BC%95%E5%B0%8E%E9%99%AA%E5%AF%A9%E5%9C%98-%E7%84%A1%E9%9C%80%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E8%AD%A6%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E6%88%96%E6%AD%A6%E5%8A%9B%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E8%88%87%E5%90%A6/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E8%25A8%258A-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E5%25BC%2595%25E5%25B0%258E%25E9%2599%25AA%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E5%259C%2598-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E9%259C%2580%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2583%25A8%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E6%2588%2596%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%258A%259B%25E5%2590%2588%25E7%2590%2586%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%2590%25A6%2F&d=kJqg1kpVOanmZM9Z9Y77dgtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=7acf1247\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E8%25A8%258A-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E5%25BC%2595%25E5%25B0%258E%25E9%2599%25AA%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E5%259C%2598-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E9%259C%2580%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2583%25A8%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E6%2588%2596%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%258A%259B%25E5%2590%2588%25E7%2590%2586%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%2590%25A6%2F&h=a1644842\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E7%BD%AA%E5%AF%A9%E8%A8%8A-%E5%AE%98%E5%BC%95%E5%B0%8E%E9%99%